No. 11-85. Amy, the Victim in the Misty Child Pornography Series, Petitioner v. Michael M. Monzel, et al. 565 U.S. 1072, 132 S. Ct. 756,

181 L. Ed. 2d 508,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8458. November 28, 2011.

Motion of respondent Michael M. Monzel for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Same case below, 395 U.S. App. D.C. 162, 641 F.3d 528.
